extends layout
	
block menu
	- var ref_page='donate'

block content
	h1 Donate
	p Well, if you like the site, or think it's in some way helpfull to you, or just if you feel really generous today, don't hesitate to leave a coin!
	p It will encourage me to go on and improve the site, like adding more drill category types or developing the 'Settings' section that will let you configure the drill generator as you like, or even giving the possibility to manage user accounts and keep to trace of all your drills!
	p Thank's for your support!
